OL,3,CCeremony of keys to take place to mark
OL,4,CKing visiting for Royal Week
OL,6,FThe traditional Ceremony of the Keys
OL,7,Fis set to take place in the Gardens of
OL,8,Fthe Palace of Holyroodhouse, marking
OL,9,Fthe start of Royal Week.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday the King and Queen will
OL,12,Fcarry out a series of engagements in
OL,13,FEdinburgh as Royal Week gets under way
OL,14,Fin Scotland.
OL,16,FThe Lord Provost Robert Aldridge will
OL,17,Fpresent the keys to the City of
OL,18,FEdinburgh to the King, who will return
OL,19,Fthem for safe keeping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
