OL,3,CCeremony of keys to take place to mark
OL,4,CKing visiting for Royal Week
OL,6,FThe King will then host an investiture
OL,7,Fceremony at the Palace with those
OL,8,Freceiving honours including forensic
OL,9,Fscientist Lorna Dawson, who was
OL,10,Fawarded a damehood in the New Year
OL,11,FHonours, and New Seekers singer Eve
OL,12,FGraham, who becomes an MBE for
OL,13,Fservices to the music industry.
OL,15,FSimon Milne, regius keeper of the
OL,16,FRoyal Botanic Garden Edinburgh,
OL,17,Freceives a knighthood for services to
OL,18,Fbotany, conservation and horticulture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
