OL,3,CCeremony of keys to take place to mark
OL,4,CKing visiting for Royal Week
OL,6,FLater that day the King and Queen,
OL,7,Faccompanied by The Duke of Edinburgh
OL,8,Fand The Princess Royal, will host a
OL,9,Fgarden party at the Palace.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday the King and Queen, The
OL,12,FDuke of Rothesay and The Duke of
OL,13,FEdinburgh will attend the Thistle
OL,14,FService at St Giles Cathedral.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
