OL,3,CCeremony of keys to take place to mark
OL,4,CKing visiting for Royal Week
OL,6,FOn Thursday the King will undertake
OL,7,Fengagements in Jedburgh which will
OL,8,Fcoincide with the Jethart Callant
OL,9,FFestival, where he will view a
OL,10,Fprocession of horses riding past the
OL,11,Ftown square and will have an
OL,12,Fopportunity to join a traditional game
OL,13,Fof "hand ba'", a historic street sport
OL,14,Fplayed annually in Jedburgh since 1704.
OL,16,FOn Friday the Duke of Edinburgh will
OL,17,Fhost a Gold Award celebration in the
OL,18,Fgardens of the Palace.
