OL,3,CCeremony of keys to take place to mark
OL,4,CKing visiting for Royal Week
OL,6,FThe monarch traditionally spends a
OL,7,Fweek based at the Palace of
OL,8,FHolyroodhouse each year in what is
OL,9,Fknown as Holyrood Week or Royal Week
OL,10,Fin Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
